Package org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.utils.opModeRegistration

Class OperationModeClassFilter

java.lang.Object
org.firstinspires.ftc.teamcode.utils.opModeRegistration.OperationModeClassFilter
All Implemented Interfaces:
org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.opmode.ClassFilter
public class OperationModeClassFilter extends Object implements org.firstinspires.ftc.robotcore.internal.opmode.ClassFilter
A ClassFilter to filter OperationModes during registration. All classes of this APK are sent through this filter, and the valid OperationModes of those classes are registered, if possible. The methods of this filter are called by a ClassManager which is responsible for managing the classes of this APK. The ClassManager is controlled by the ClassManagerFactory which is managed by the OperationModeRegistrar which is managed by a Thread spawned by the app at runtime.
